---

WHEN TO USE GSAP

Use GSAP in these sections:

Hero section
Scroll reveal
Text animation
Image animation
Section transitions
Parallax effects
Hover animation
Page transitions
Loading animation
Feature sections
Call to action sections

Avoid GSAP in:

Forms
Simple buttons
Static layouts
Small UI elements

---

REACT + GSAP RULES

Always use:

gsap
gsap/ScrollTrigger
useEffect or useLayoutEffect
useRef

Always register plugin:

gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger)

Use useRef for elements.

Never manipulate DOM directly.

Always use scoped animations.

Example structure:

const sectionRef = useRef()

useLayoutEffect(() => {

  const ctx = gsap.context(() => {

    gsap.from(...)

  }, sectionRef)

  return () => ctx.revert()

}, [])

