HERO ANIMATION RULES

Hero should always have:

Text fade up
Heading reveal
Subheading fade
Button slide up
Image scale or parallax
Background subtle motion

Animation timing:

delay 0.2
stagger 0.1
duration 1
ease power3.out

No aggressive motion.

Smooth cinematic entrance.

---

SCROLL ANIMATION RULES

Every section should reveal on scroll.

Use:

ScrollTrigger

Start:

top 80%

End:

top 50%

Animation types:

fade up
slide up
scale in
image reveal
text reveal

Example:

gsap.from(".section", {
  opacity: 0,
  y: 50,
  duration: 1,
  scrollTrigger: {
    trigger: ".section",
    start: "top 80%"
  }
})

